<HEADLINE>
<P>
CONDUCTOR BERNSTEIN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I give Bernstein much of the credit for my lifelong appreciation of good music. 
</P>
<P>
Many years ago, when I was very young, I watched his lectures on "Omnibus" and 
thought he was just the coolest thing I'd ever seen. He convinced this 
schoolgirl, on her relentless quest for hipness, that you could love classical 
music without being square. I'm sure I'm joined by millions in being immensely 
grateful for the wonderful gift that was Leonard Bernstein. Thanks, Lenny, and 
Godspeed. 
</P>
<P>
PATRICIA van HARTESVELDT 
</P>
<P>
Reseda 
</P>
</TEXT>
