<P>
Wild Art 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA102690-0036 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 298044 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 26, 1990, Friday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
