welcomed back by niece Jackie Heyne, right, and sister-in-law Millie Taylor at 
LAX. He was freed by Iraq because of his medical conditions. ANACLETO RAPPING / 
Los Angeles Times; Photo, Former hostage Jack Frazier, far left, is swarmed by 
the media at Los Angeles International Airport. MARK BOSTER / Los Angeles Times 
